NAME
    Catalyst::Plugin::Spark::Form - A simple plug-in to make forms
    accessible quickly off the CTX.

VERSION
    version 0.01000002

SYNOPSIS
      use Catalyst qw/ Spark::Form /;

      ...

      sub action {
        my ( $self, $ctx, @rest ) = @_;

        $ctx->form('bar') # loads My::Project::Form::Bar or My::Project::F::Bar

      }

METHODS
  form
      $ctx->form( $formname )

CREDITS
    Code thrown together by James Laver <http://jameslaver.com>.

    Code stolen from $c->controller.

DISCLAIMER
    The code mightn't work, but its not my fault if it doesn't. Will gladly
    accept patches.

